<center>
   <br><br>
   <h1>Advantages and Disadvantages of Custom Tags</h1>
   <br>
</center> 
<font size=4>
<ul>
   <li>Advantages</li>
   <ul>
      <li>Simple to use.</li>
      <li>Naturally portable.</li>
      <li>Perfect for creating templates and further separating Java code
          from presentation logic.</li>
   </ul>
   <li>Disadvantages</li>
   <ul>
      <li>Complexity.</li>
      <li>Hard to setup.</li>
      <li>Limited for JSP page programming.</li>
   </ul>
</ul>
</font>
